additional_data.description: The spirit of the largest amethyst geode in the world.  She is honest and noble empress, to be certain, but she has a "shoot first, ask questions later" wild side to her as well. She often goes running off into groups of enemies by herself, causing headaches for all her allies. But she always thinks she's in the right and never doubts herself.
additional_data.how_to_acquire:
◦ "Jewels and The Secret Workshop" Event: Clear Chapter 3
◦ "Jewels and The Secret Workshop" Event: Exchange for 1000 Pyroxene Shards
◦The cost increases by 100 Pyroxene Shards after each exchange (1000, 1100, 1200, 1300)
additional_data.notes_and_trivia: ◦ Slightly increases the drop rate of Pyroxene Shards during the "Jewels and The Secret Workshop" event.

main: "I'm an honest gal, by all accounts!"
summon: "I'm going for it! Justice is on my side!"
limit_break: "This is for my own peace of mind!"
